{"word":"G1520 - εἷς - heîs - hice - One","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εἷς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">heîs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hice</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">One</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஒரு, ஒன்று, ஒருமைப்பாடு - எண்குறி"},{"paragraph":"one"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>(Including the neuter [etc.] <b>&#x03B5;&#x0314;&#x0301;&#x03BD;</b> <b>hen</b>); a primary numeral; <i>one</i>: - a (-n, -ny, certain), + abundantly, man, one (another), only, other, some. See also <a href=\"#/G1527 - εἷς καθ’ εἷς - heîs kath’ heîs - hice kath hice/1527\">G1527</a>, <a href=\"#/G3367 - μηδείς - mēdeís - may-dice'/3367\">G3367</a>, <a href=\"#/G3391 - μία - mía - mee'-ah/3391\">G3391</a>, <a href=\"#/G3762 - οὐδείς - oudeís - oo-dice'/3762\">G3762</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}